# Pizza Sales Analysis Dashboard

## 📌 Overview
This project analyzes pizza sales data to identify revenue trends, customer behavior, and key business performance metrics. The goal is to derive actionable insights that can support data-driven decision-making.

## 🎯 Objective
- Track overall revenue and sales performance
- Identify peak sales hours and high-demand products
- Analyze customer ordering patterns
- Create KPIs to monitor business performance

## 🛠 Tools & Technologies
- SQL (Data Extraction & Querying)
- Excel (Data Cleaning & Preprocessing)
- Power BI (Interactive Dashboard & Visualization)

## 📊 Key KPIs
- Total Revenue
- Total Orders
- Average Order Value
- Top-Selling Pizzas
- Peak Sales Hours

## 🔍 Analysis Performed
- Sales trend analysis over time
- Category-wise and product-wise performance
- Peak hour and high-demand period identification
- Customer ordering behavior insights

## 📈 Key Insights
- Identified top-performing pizza categories contributing the highest revenue
- Peak order volume observed during specific hours, indicating demand patterns
- Certain products consistently outperformed others, helping optimize inventory decisions

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- Interactive filters for category and time-based analysis
- Visual representation of KPIs and trends
- User-friendly layout for quick business insights

## 📂 Project Structure
- SQL queries
- Cleaned dataset (Excel)
- Power BI dashboard file

## 🚀 Impact
- Improved understanding of sales patterns and customer preferences
- Enabled data-driven decisions for product and sales strategy
